snippet.title: Hollyscoop
snippet.description:
Whether it's Selena Gomez, Gigi Hadid, Justin Bieber, or the Kardashians, we're committed to providing you with information on all your favorite actors, singers and A-listers as soon as it breaks. At HOLLYSCOOP we're obsessed with celebrities, TV, music, movies, and of course… Hollywood!

It's nonstop, wall-to-wall celeb coverage, and we invite you to join the conversation! Find it all on Hollyscoop!
